Trade/Device Name(s): UniStrip1™ Generic Blood Glucose Test Strips
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): OneTouch® UltraSmart® meters (purchased before April 2016, calibration code 49)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for UniStrip1™ Generic Blood Glucose Test Strips for use with select OneTouch® Ultra® family meters to measure glucose in capillary whole blood
Indications for Use Summary: For self-testing by people with diabetes to quantitatively measure glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from the finger, palm, or forearm using compatible OneTouch® Ultra® meters purchased before April 2016, as an aid to monitor diabetes control; not for diagnosis, screening, or use on neonates.
